---
title: California Pulled Chicken Sammie with Kale and  Cucumber Salad
description: Tonight's 20 min meal will have you riding a wave to the west coast! Smashed avocado, lemon aioli, tomatoes, and pulled chicken are all layered between toasted artisan buns. A crisp summer salad brimming with cucumber and toasted seeds will have you checking off every part of the food pyramid.
